Debugging
--------------------
/var/www/js-html/weather/server$ node run.js & //Start background process
killall -s KILL node



MONGO Create Admin user
-----------------
1. Stop Mongo
$sudo systemctl stop mongodb

2. In mongod.conf, uncomment #security: authorization: enabled
$nano /etc/mongod.conf 

3. Restart Mongo
sudo systemctl start mongodb

4. Create Admin User with all rights
use admin
db.createUser({ user: "mongoadmin" , pwd: "denied1234", roles: ["userAdminAnyDatabase", "dbAdminAnyDatabase", "readWriteAnyDatabase"]})

5. Stop Mongo
$sudo systemctl stop mongodb

6. In mongod.conf, revert to security: authorization: enabled
$nano /etc/mongod.conf 

7. Restart Mongo
sudo systemctl start mongodb

8. Login
mongo admin -u irfan -p denied1234